              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p class="light-gray">
                <strong>Phyto Corrective Masque</strong><br>
                Provide immediate relief to stressed, redness-prone skin with this intensive hydration mask. Infused
                with soothing botanicals and hyaluronic acid, it calms irritation and replenishes moisture for a smooth,
